{"about_the_game":"Craft wands, create synergies, battle monsters, and survive. Dive into the depths of magic crafting in Wandness, where you'll forge spells from magical components and elemental gems for endless combinations. Explore procedurally generated dungeons, defeat bosses, and unleash your magic madness to overcome the darkness that threatens to rule the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Craft Spells</h2>Mix over 50 magical components to make unique and powerful wands that change how over 20 projectiles behave.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928690/extras/WandsGif.gif?t=1739082087\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Create Synergies</h2>Use elemental gems in wands, combined with their class, to make a lot of powerful combinations that work well to power your attacks.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928690/extras/AC.gif?t=1739082087\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Survive</h2>Fight off waves of enemies at each node until the portal recharges, letting you teleport safely to go deeper into the dark.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928690/extras/FightGif.gif?t=1739082087\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2>\ud83c\udfb2 Randomized Gameplay from Infinite spells possibilities<br>\ud83e\udde0 A lot of synergies to discover between the elements and classes.<br>\u2694\ufe0f Defeat the darkness and survive the monster horde<br>\ud83c\udfb2 Random Generated maps and encounters<br>\u231b 40-60 minutes action-packed sessions.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928690/extras/mapGif.gif?t=1739082087\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739082087","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/29